thrilling risk-reward holes.\nSet against a rustic canyon backdrop, and inspired by old western mining towns, each hole presents a new, exhilarating challenge that will test even the most seasoned golfers.\n\n## New HD User Interface\n- A new menu look, as well as HD treatment to all interactive and visual screens.\n* Quest 2 players will have the main menu HD off by default. Same as in live currently, turning it on in the settings will have a performance hit. With it off, the main menu will be standard definition when you have a club in hand to hit, and will change to HD when have controller in hand to interact with menu.\n\n## Sweetens Cove 10th Anniversary Major\n- The GOLF+ Tour will head to Sweetens Cove on 10/31 for the Major of the season. The weekly tournament will have a 3x Points Multiplier. No multiplier for daily tournaments. \n\n## No Laying Up - Hole In One Challenge\nIn partnership with 'No Laying Up', Challenges the week of 10/28 on Sweetens Cove will have a Hole In One contest.\n- Everyone who completes the Hole-in-One challenge will unlock Sweetens Cove.\n- 5 Players with a HIO will receive a $100 Credit to the No Laying Up Pro Shop.\n- 4 G+ Pass members with a HIO will win a Day Pass to Sweetens Cove - In real life ; )\n* Must have a GOLF+ email account to be eligible. GOLF+ PASS trial members eligible. Contest rules at www.golfplusvr.com/terms-and-conditions apply.", "created_date": 1729878252, "id": "8465138256914846", "version": "771.2", "version_code": 11733, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 68}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "2412327085529357", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8465138256914846"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "2309851355956647"}]}, "change_log": "New Update v771.15 is Live!\n\n## New Course: Canyons\nIntroducing Canyons, a GOLF+ original design where you'll navigate dramatic elevation changes and face a series of thrilling risk-reward holes.\nSet against a rustic canyon backdrop, and inspired by old western mining towns, each hole presents a new, exhilarating challenge that will test even the most seasoned golfers.\n\n## New HD User Interface\n- A new menu look, as well as HD treatment to all interactive and visual screens.\n* Quest 2 players will have the main menu HD off by default. Same as in live currently, turning it on in the settings will have a performance hit. With it off, the main menu will be standard definition when you have a club in hand to hit, and will change to HD when have controller in hand to interact with menu.\n\n## Sweetens Cove 10th Anniversary Major\n- The GOLF+ Tour will head to Sweetens Cove on 10/31 for the Major of the season. The weekly tournament will have a 3x Points Multiplier. No multiplier for daily tournaments. \n\n## No Laying Up - Hole In One Challenge\nIn partnership with 'No Laying Up', Challenges the week of 10/28 on Sweetens Cove will have a Hole In One contest.\n- Everyone who completes the Hole-in-One challenge will unlock Sweetens Cove.\n- 5 Players with a HIO will receive a $100 Credit to the No Laying Up Pro Shop.\n- 4 G+ Pass members with a HIO will win a Day Pass to Sweetens Cove - In real life ; )\n* Must have a GOLF+ email account to be eligible. GOLF+ PASS trial members eligible. Contest rules at www.golfplusvr.com/terms-and-conditions apply.", "created_date": 1729803735, "id": "8459152847513387", "version": "771.15", "version_code": 11732, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 68}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "Androi